snippet.title: Nintendo DS Longplay [143] FIFA World Cup 2006 (EU)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mariofan98

I had this version as a child with eight years.

I've already recorded the GBA version in 2016, this is now the DS version to compare with it and with four buttons at the right side of the handheld it feels better to play with it.

Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
